text: Rino Falk Larsen (born 14 February 1996) is a Norwegian professional footballer who currently plays for Kjelsås. ==Club career== He started his career in Drøbak-Frogn IL, and played for the senior team as early as 2011, aged 15. He joined Vålerenga in late 2012, and after several years in their junior system, he reached the first-team bench on one occasion in 2015 and made his Norwegian Premier League debut in May 2016 against Strømsgodset.
